data.description:
This charming bungalow-style residence is the perfect place to call home! Offering ample living space, this home features a bonus room that can serve as a study, TV room, or office, complete with its own separate entrance for added convenience. As the colder fall and winter nights approach, you'll relish the warmth of the living room's cozy fireplace, creating a welcoming atmosphere.

Step outside onto your private deck, surrounded by lush greenery and just the right-sized yard for your outdoor enjoyment. The unfinished basement presents a world of possibilities, awaiting your creative touch to transform it into an additional entertainment space, a hobby room, or even a home gym.

Nestled on a tranquil street, this residence boasts a prime location with a picturesque park just steps away. This wonderful home is eagerly awaiting its next owner, and you won't want to miss the opportunity to make it yours.
